posting_body: ['ANOTHER PROPERTY PROFESSIONALLY MANAGED BY PRO REALTY SERVICES', 'Recently Remodeled 4 Bedroom **Half off August Rent with an August 2022 Move', 'In**', 'Property Address', '10407 Quebec Ave S | Bloomington, MN 55348', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'PRO Realty Services |', 'show contact info', 'Description', '**Half off August Rent with an August 2022 Move', 'In**', '4 bedroom, 1 and 3/4 bathroom twinhome with a beautiful kitchen, bonus living room space, and in-unit laundry!', 'This home has a split level entry, with two of the bedrooms located upstairs and two of the bedrooms located on the lower level.', 'Some other great features include central air, a dishwasher, off-street parking, and a 2 car attached garage!', 'Video Link: <URL>', 'SHOWINGS: Go here to apply or schedule a showing: prs.rentals', 'or call Carmen with PRO Realty Services today at', 'show contact info', '!', 'Utilities paid by resident: Gas, Electric, Water/Sewer, & Trash.', 'Many homes for rent are currently occupied.', 'Please respect the convenience and privacy of our residents.', 'Showings are by appointment only.', 'One month rent and security deposit due at lease signing.', 'Qualifications: Max occupants: 8.', 'Must have satisfactory rental history, must pass criminal history background check and must have documented income of 2.5 times the monthly rent, pet not accepted, no recent evictions.', 'Property is not Section 8.', 'Please see detailed rental criteria on our application.', 'Amenities', 'Central Air', 'Yard Space', 'Dishwasher', 'In Unit Laundry', 'Off-Street Parking', '2-Car Attached Garage', 'Bonus Living Room Space', 'Seperate Living/Dining Areas', 'Stainless Steel Refrigerator & Electric Stove', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 4BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,700', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,395.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,395.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
